1065.0   = G, Gravity (cm/s**2)
2.214    = FSCALE, stellar flux scaling (Seff); Earth=1.0
0.250    = ALB, Surface Albedo
0.00e+00 = ZTROP, height of the tropopause (cm)
0.00     = FAR, Ar partial pressure
6.995E8  = R0, radius of planet (cm)
0.010    = P0, surface pressure (bar)
VENUS    = PLANET, string naming planet type
0.000    = TIMEGA, for modifying solar flux (SUN ONLY)
0        = IRESET
33       = MSUN
0        = IHZSCALE (set to 1 for SED-dep scaling)
0.46E5   = DZGRID [cm]







